Входящие письма могут содержать элементы, позволяющие отправителю скрытно отслеживать действия с письмом, в частности, время просмотра и некоторые параметры устройства, на котором письмо было прочитано. К небезопасным элементам относятся, например, загружаемые из Интернета картинки письма или встроенные скрипты. В целях безопасности такие элементы автоматически отключаются при просмотре письма.

Incoming email messages can contain elements that allow a sender to secretly track actions with the message, in particular, a view time and some parameters of the device the message was read from. Insecure elements include, for example, images downloaded from the Internet or embedded scripts. For security reasons, such items are automatically disabled when viewing the message.

Settings.QueryText: SELECT CASE WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Ref REFS Document.Meeting THEN CASE WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.DeletionMark THEN 10 ELSE 0 END WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Ref REFS Document.PlannedInteraction THEN CASE WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.DeletionMark THEN 11 ELSE 1 END WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Ref REFS Document.PhoneCall THEN CASE WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.DeletionMark THEN 12 ELSE 2 END WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Ref REFS Document.IncomingEmail THEN CASE WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.DeletionMark THEN 13 ELSE 3 END WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Ref REFS Document.OutgoingEmail THEN CASE WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.DeletionMark THEN 14 ELSE CASE WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.OutgoingEmailStatus = VALUE(Enum.OutgoingEmailStatuses.Draft) THEN 15 WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.OutgoingEmailStatus = VALUE(Enum.OutgoingEmailStatuses.Outgoing) THEN 16 ELSE 4 END END WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Ref REFS Document.SMSMessage THEN CASE WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.DeletionMark THEN 22 ELSE CASE WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.OutgoingEmailStatus = VALUE(Enum.SMSMessageDocumentState.Draft) THEN 17 WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.OutgoingEmailStatus = VALUE(Enum.SMSMessageDocumentState.Outgoing) THEN 18 WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.OutgoingEmailStatus = VALUE(Enum.SMSMessageDocumentState.DeliveryInProgress) THEN 19 WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.OutgoingEmailStatus = VALUE(Enum.SMSMessageDocumentState.PartiallyDelivered) THEN 21 WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.OutgoingEmailStatus = VALUE(Enum.SMSMessageDocumentState.NotDelivered) THEN 23 WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.OutgoingEmailStatus = VALUE(Enum.SMSMessageDocumentState.Delivered) THEN 24 ELSE 17 END END END AS PictureNumber, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Ref, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Date, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.DeletionMark, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Number, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Author, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Incoming, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Subject, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.EmployeeResponsible AS EmployeeResponsible, ISNULL(InteractionsSubjectsOverridable.Reviewed, False) AS Reviewed, ISNULL(InteractionsSubjectsOverridable.ReviewAfter, DateTime(1,1,1)) AS ReviewAfter, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Members, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Type, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.OutgoingEmailStatus, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.HasAttachments, ISNULL(InteractionsSubjectsOverridable.Topic, UNDEFINED) AS Topic, VALUETYPE(InteractionsSubjectsOverridable.Topic) AS SubjectType, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Account, ISNULL(InteractionsSubjectsOverridable.EmailMessageFolder, VALUE(Catalog.EmailMessageFolders.EmptyRef)) AS Folder, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.SentReceived AS SentReceived, CAST(InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Size / 1024 AS NUMBER(10, 2)) AS Size, InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Importance, CASE WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Importance = VALUE(Enum.InteractionImportanceOptions.High) THEN 2 WHEN InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Importance = VALUE(Enum.InteractionImportanceOptions.Low) THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS ImportancePictureNumber FROM DocumentJournal.Interactions AS InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable LEFT JOIN InformationRegister.InteractionsFolderSubjects AS InteractionsSubjectsOverridable ON InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Ref = InteractionsSubjectsOverridable.Interaction {WHERE InteractionDocumentsLogOverridable.Ref AS Search}

SELECT DISTINCT InteractionsSubjectsStatesOverridable.Topic AS Topic, InteractionsSubjectsStatesOverridable.NotReviewedInteractionsCount AS NotReviewedInteractionsCount, InteractionsSubjectsStatesOverridable.IsActive AS IsActive, InteractionsSubjectsStatesOverridable.LastInteractionDate AS LastInteractionDate, VALUETYPE(InteractionsSubjectsStatesOverridable.Topic) AS SubjectType FROM InformationRegister.InteractionsSubjectsStates AS InteractionsSubjectsStatesOverridable INNER JOIN InformationRegister.InteractionsFolderSubjects AS InteractionsFolderSubjectsOverridable INNER JOIN DocumentJournal.Interactions AS InteractionsOverridable ON InteractionsFolderSubjectsOverridable.Interaction = InteractionsOverridable.Ref ON InteractionsSubjectsStatesOverridable.Topic = InteractionsFolderSubjectsOverridable.Topic {WHERE InteractionsOverridable.EmployeeResponsible, InteractionsOverridable.Type, InteractionsOverridable.Importance, InteractionsOverridable.OutgoingEmailStatus, InteractionsOverridable.Account, InteractionsOverridable.Author, InteractionsOverridable.DeletionMark, InteractionsOverridable.Incoming, InteractionsFolderSubjectsOverridable.Reviewed, InteractionsFolderSubjectsOverridable.ReviewAfter}

SELECT DISTINCT InteractionsContactsStatesOverridable.Contact AS Contact, InteractionsContactsStatesOverridable.NotReviewedInteractionsCount AS NotReviewedInteractionsCount, InteractionsContactsStatesOverridable.LastInteractionDate AS LastInteractionDate, VALUETYPE(InteractionsContactsStatesOverridable.Contact) AS ContactType FROM InformationRegister.InteractionsContactStates AS InteractionsContactsStatesOverridable {INNER JOIN InformationRegister.InteractionsContacts AS InteractionsContactsOverridable INNER JOIN InformationRegister.InteractionsFolderSubjects AS InteractionsFolderSubjectsOverridable ON InteractionsContactsOverridable.Interaction = InteractionsFolderSubjectsOverridable.Interaction INNER JOIN DocumentJournal.Interactions AS InteractionsOverridable ON InteractionsContactsOverridable.Interaction = InteractionsOverridable.Ref ON InteractionsContactsStatesOverridable.Contact = InteractionsContactsOverridable.Contact} {WHERE InteractionsOverridable.EmployeeResponsible, InteractionsOverridable.Type, InteractionsOverridable.Importance, InteractionsOverridable.OutgoingEmailStatus, InteractionsOverridable.Account, InteractionsOverridable.Author, InteractionsOverridable.Incoming, InteractionsFolderSubjectsOverridable.Reviewed, InteractionsFolderSubjectsOverridable.ReviewAfter}
